01:08:50.270 --> 01:08:54.200
So just to belabor
the point again,

01:08:54.200 --> 01:08:57.970
the way that you measure
in principle is common.

01:08:57.970 --> 01:09:01.210
And then you can zoom
in and out depending

01:09:01.210 --> 01:09:07.060
