01:11:16.690 --> 01:11:20.590
This is another sort of
genre in the literature.

01:11:20.590 --> 01:11:23.080
This is financial--
this one takes

01:11:23.080 --> 01:11:27.280
the expansion of the
financial system as exogenous.

01:11:27.280 --> 01:11:30.700
This one tries to
make it endogenous.

01:11:30.700 --> 01:11:33.550
Key contributors
are, say for example,

01:11:33.550 --> 01:11:36.970
Greenwood and Jovanovic,
